"title": "3050: Holy Spirit, wisdom of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3050: holy spirit, wisdom of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of being discerning and perceptive which is a characteristic of the Holy Spirit. The Holy Spirit is the source of human wisdom.</p>\n<h2>Those who knew and can know the wisdom of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Joshua</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a></strong> <em>Either a wise human spirit or the Spirit of God who gives wisdom (NIV footnote).</em></p>\n<h3>The Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:40\">LUK 2:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:9\">COL 2:9</a> <em>“fulness” includes wisdom.</em></p>\n<h3>Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is the source of wisdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:6-Job32:9\">JOB 32:6–32:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:9-Acts6:10\">ACT 6:9–6:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12-1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:12–2:14</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:8-1Kgs3:9\">1KI 3:8–3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:12\">1KI 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29-1Kgs4:34\">1KI 4:29–4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1\">1KI 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:23-1Kgs10:24\">1KI 10:23–10:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:6\">PRO 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:10-Dan5:16\">DAN 5:10–5:16</a> <em>Daniel's wisdom</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:3\">ACT 6:3</a> <em>the choosing of the Seven</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:11\">1CO 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8\">1CO 12:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit as teacher</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:19-Matt10:20\">MAT 10:19–10:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:11\">MRK 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:27\">1JN 2:27</a></p>",
